snippet.title: Introducing iPhone 16 Pro | Apple
snippet.description:
This is iPhone 16 Pro. Built for Apple Intelligence. A new powerful, private, personal, deeply integrated intelligence system to help you get things done effortlessly.

Powered by the new supercharged A18 Pro chip, with a faster Neural Engine, and an improved CPU and GPU. Which levels up both your iPhone and your gaming experience, offering our best-ever graphics performance.

Plus thereâ€™s an all-new camera system and an all-new way to control it. Use Camera Control to instantly access your camera, adjust settings, and take a photo.

And you can now shoot video in 4K 120 fps Dolby Vision to capture and edit stunningly cinematic slow motion.

Built with titanium. And featuring our thinnest borders for an even larger display.

iPhone 16 Pro is the most innovative, most powerful, and most intelligent iPhone ever. From the inside out.

snippet.title: The GOAT Roast ğŸğŸ’¥ | Plip Plip
snippet.description:
"The GOAT" (The Goofiest Of All Time) is a Tamil film that falls under the 'milking' genre. Staying true to the genre, Venkat Prabhu has given a compilation of 'brainrot reels' that tries to harvest nostalgia, disguised as a movie. Thalapathy, Ilaya Thalapathy, Ilalaya Thalapathy and Ilalalaya Thalapathy have played pivotal roles in this goofy ahh film.

snippet.description:
First of all HAPPY GANESH CHATURTHIğŸ™ğŸ™
Well this generation has changed so much. Me and Shyam being a millennials but having GENZ friends gave us this insight about them. 
Hum bhi kahin na kahin GenZ ke saath rehke same harkatein karne lag gaye hai ğŸ˜…
But this video is pure exaggeration, GenZ itne bhi danger nahi hote hai.  Please take it in a funny way only.
Hum toh khud GenZ jaise rehte hai. 
Hope you enjoyed our take on this new generation.

In Venom: The Last Dance, Tom Hardy returns as Venom, one of Marvelâ€™s greatest and most complex characters, for the final film in the trilogy. Eddie and Venom are on the run. Hunted by both of their worlds and with the net closing in, the duo are forced into a devastating decision that will bring the curtains down on Venom and Eddie's last dance.
 
Venom: The Last Dance stars Tom Hardy, Chiwetel Ejiofor, Juno Temple, Rhys Ifans, Peggy Lu, Alanna Ubach and Stephen Graham. snippet.title: Deva Shree Ganesha - 8K/4K Video | Ganpati Song | Agneepath | Priyanka Chopra | Hrithik Roshan
snippet.description:
Experience the divine energy and vibrant spirit of Ganesh Chaturthi with the mesmerizing 8K/4K video of "Deva Shree Ganesha" from the blockbuster movie Agneepath. 
 
#devashreeganesha #hrithikroshan #priyankachopra #agneepath #ajayatul #ajaygogavale #ganeshsongs #ganpatisongs #ganpatibappamorya 

Credits :
Song Title- Deva Shree Ganesha 
Movie- Agneepath (2012) 
Singer- Ajay Gogavale 
Lyrics- Amitabh Bhattacharya 
Music- Ajay-Atul
Video remastered by @MusicRemaster 

Song Lyrics :
Jwaala Si Jalti Hai Aankhon Mein Jiske Bhi
Dil Mein Tera Naam Hai
Parwah Hi Kya Uska Aarambh Kaisa Hai
Aur Kaisa Parinam Hai
Dharti Ambar Sitaare
Uski Nazarein Utaarein
Dar Bhi Us Se Daraa Re
Jiski Rakhwaliyan Re Karta Saya Tera
Deva Shree Ganesha (X8)

Ho Teri Bhakti Ka Vardan Hai
Jo Kamaye Wo Dhanwan Hai
Bin Kinaare Ki Kashti Hai Woh
Deva Tujhse Jo Anjaan Hai
Yoon To Mooshak Sawari Teri
Sab Pe Hai Peharedaari Teri
Paap Ki Aandhiyan Laakh Hon
Kabhi Jyoti Na Haari Teri
Apni Takdeer Ka Woh Khud Sikandar Hua Re
Bhool Ke Yeh Jahan Re Jis Kisi Ne Yahan Re
Saath Paaya Tera Hey
Deva Shree Ganesha X (8)

Ho Teri Dhooli Ka Teeka Kiye
Deva Jo Bhakt Tera Jiye
Use Amrit Ka Hai Moh Kya
Hans Ke Vish Ka Woh Pyaala Piye
Teri Mahima Ke Chhaya Tale
Kaal Ke Rath Ka Pahiya Chale
Ek Chingari Pratishodh Se
Khadi Raavan Ki Lanka Jale
Shatruon Ki Kataarein Ik Akele Se Haarein
Kan Bhi Parbat Hua Re, Shlok Ban Ke Jahan Re
Naam Aaya Tera Hey
Deva Shree Ganesha X (8)

Ganpati Bappa Moreya
Ghalin Lotangan Vandin Charan
Dolyani Pahin Rup Tujhe
Deva Preme Alingan Anande Pujin
Bhave Ovaleen Mhane Nama

Twameva Mata,Cha Phita Twameva
Twameva Bandhuscha Sakha Twamevaa....
Twameva Vidya,Dravinum Twameva
Twameva Sarvam Mama Deva Devaaa

Kayena Vacha Manasendriyenva
Buddhyatmana Va Prakritiswabhavat
Karoomi Yadhyath Sakalam Parasmai
Narayanayeti Samarpayami

Achyutam Keshavam Ramnarayanam
Krushanadamodaram Vasudevam Bhaje
Shridharam Madhavam Gopikavallabham
Janaki Nayakam Ramchandra Bhaje

Hare Raam Hare Raam
Raam Raam Hare Hareee
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna
Krishna Krishna Hare Hareee
Hare Raam Hare Raam
Raam Raam Hare Hareeee
Hare Krishna Hare Krishna
Krishna Krishna Hare Hareee

Kaffara Episode 43 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 8th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove sheâ€™s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainmentâ€™s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznaviâ€™s love?

This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznaviâ€™s love?

Kaffara Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 7th September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove sheâ€™s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

In this video, YouTuber Bristi Gupta aka (Bristi Home Kitchen)  shares her inspiring journey of growing her YouTube channel from 300,000 to 1 million subscribers in just nine days during the lockdown. She recalls a shocking moment when her brother informed her that her channel was hacked, wiping out all her earnings.

 Bristi talks about her middle-class family, where her father ran a flour mill, and her mother was a homemaker. Initially lacking confidence to speak on camera, she decided to create cooking videos without her voice, using only music, and uploaded her first video on August 16, 2018. Despite personal challenges, including her fatherâ€™s illness, she persevered and grew her channel to 1.2 million subscribers in just four months. 

Today, with over 5.3 million subscribers, Bristi uploads popular food and cake recipes on her channel, inspiring many. Her story demonstrates how a woman can work from home and inspire others, especially women striving to fulfill their dreams after marriage. Bristi is a role model for every woman seeking to turn her aspirations into reality.

Her Channel - @BristiHomeKitchen

snippet.title: Taaza Khabar | Season 2 | Official Trailer | Hotstar Specials | Sept 27 | BB Ki Vines Productions
snippet.description:
Don't forget to watch the series "Taaza Khabar" starring Bhuvan Bam, streaming exclusively on Disney+ Hotstar! http://www.hotstar.com/1260127221

Karza aur gunah chukaane padhte hain! Kabhi kabhi marr ke bhi..

Vardaan ya shraap? Kismat ya mehnat? Jeevan ya maut?
Vasya ki kahani ka naya adhyay dekhiye Hotstar Specials Taaza Khabar Season 2 mein, streaming from September 27, only on Disney+ Hotstar.

Disney+ Hotstar's hit fantasy-drama series returns with Hotstar Specials presents Taaza Khabar Season 2, diving deeper into the consequences of Vasya's miraculous gift. Set against the gritty backdrop of Mumbai, this season promises to take viewers on an intense journey as Vasya grapples with the loss of his power and faces life-threatening challenges.

Directed by Himank Gaur and produced by Rohit Raj & Bhuvan Bam under BB Ki Vines Productions, the show continues to be penned by the talented writer duo Hussain Dalal & Abbas Dalal. Bhuvan Bam reprises his role as Vasant Gawde, joined by Shriya Pilgaonkar, Mahesh Manjrekar, Jaaved Jaaferi, Deven Bhojani, Shilpa Shukla, Prathmesh Parab, and Nitya Mathur in pivotal roles.

This season explores the thin line between blessing and curse as Vasya navigates a world where his actions have far-reaching consequences. With higher stakes and deeper emotional complexity, Taaza Khabar Season 2 promises to deliver a gripping tale of redemption, morality, and the human spirit's resilience in the face of adversity.

#TaazaKhabarSeason2 #BBKiVinesProductions #BhuvanBam

snippet.title: CARAMEL PUDDING CAKE | Bread Caramel Pudding Cake Recipe Cooking In Village | Custard Pudding Recipe
snippet.description: Today in our village, we make caramel pudding cake using bread and eggs. We bake the mixing for 2 hours in our open cooking vessel then we freeze it in the cooling. Finally, we enjoyed the cake in the evening!

About Mithijhora : 
__________________________

The show's story revolves around the lives of three sisters, Raipurna, Nilanjana, and Srotoswini. Following the sudden demise of their father, Kingshuk, Rai takes over the role of the main breadwinner for the family. Vikram, their elder brother, has physical challenges. There's a beautiful sisterhood bond between Rai, Nilu, and Srot. Rai is motivated more by her love for her sibling than by her obligation to provide for her family, nevertheless she works hard to support them.

snippet.title: How To Make Better Decisions? By Sandeep Maheshwari | Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.title: A Minecraft Movie | Teaser
snippet.description:
Be There and Be Square. #MinecraftMovie - only in theaters 2025

From Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures and starring Jason Momoa and Jack Black, â€œA Minecraft Movie,â€ directed by Jared Hess, is the first-ever big screen, live-action adaptation of Minecraft, the best-selling video game of all time.

The film also stars Emma Myers (â€œWednesdayâ€), Oscar nominee Danielle Brooks (â€œThe Color Purpleâ€), Sebastian Eugene Hansen (â€œJust Mercy, â€œLiseyâ€™s Storyâ€), with Jennifer Coolidge.

Welcome to the world of Minecraft, where creativity doesnâ€™t just help you craft, itâ€™s essential to oneâ€™s survival!  Four misfitsâ€”Garrett â€œThe Garbage Manâ€ Garrison (Momoa), Henry (Hansen), Natalie (Myers) and Dawn (Brooks)â€”find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination.  To get back home, theyâ€™ll have to master this world (and protect it from evil things like Piglins and Zombies, too) while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve (Black).  Together, their adventure will challenge all five to be bold and to reconnect with the qualities that make each of them uniquely creativeâ€¦the very skills they need to thrive back in the real world. 

Oscar nominee Hess (â€œNinety-Five Senses,â€ â€œNacho Libreâ€) directed, with Roy Lee, Jon Berg, Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Jason Momoa, Jill Messick, Torfi Frans Olafsson and Vu Bui producing, and Todd Hallowell, Kayleen Walters, Brian Mendoza, Jonathan Spaihts, Pete Chiappetta, Andrew Lary and Anthony Tittanegro executive producing.

The directorâ€™s creative team behind the camera includes BAFTA-nominated director of photography Enrique Chediak (â€œ127 Hours,â€ â€œTransformers: Rise of the Beastsâ€), Oscar-winning production designer Grant Major (â€œThe Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King,â€ â€œThe Megâ€), editor James Thomas (â€œPokÃ©mon: Detective Pikachuâ€, the â€œBoratâ€ films), Oscar-winning VFX supervisor Dan Lemmon (â€œThe Jungle Book,â€ â€œThe Batmanâ€), and costume designer Amanda Neale (â€œThe Meg,â€ â€œWhat We Do in the Shadowsâ€).  Casting is by Rachel Tenner.  The music supervisors are Gabe Hilfer and Karyn Rachtman, and the music is by Mark Mothersbaugh (â€œThor: Ragnarok,â€ the â€œLEGOÂ®â€ movies).

Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures Present A Vertigo Entertainment/On The Roam/MojÃ¤ng Aktiebolag Production, A Jared Hess Film, â€œA Minecraft Movie.â€  The film will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures worldwide and by Legendary East in China, and released only in theaters and IMAX in North America on April 4, 2025, and internationally beginning 2 April 2025.

He seamlessly switches between contrasting characters, adding depth and charisma that keeps viewers hooked. Yuvan Shankar Rajaâ€™s background score is a perfect blend, elevating every scene with pulsating beats that amplify the film's intensity and emotional core.

The screenplay is tight and engaging, with unexpected twists that keep the audience on their toes. Charnon Ki Saugandh (1988) Part -1 | Mithun Chakraborty, Amrita Singh | Blockbuster Action Movie

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a Bollywood movie released in 1988, featuring Mithun Chakraborty in the lead role. Directed by K. Bapaiah, the film falls into the action and drama genres. Here's a brief synopsis of the movie:

The film revolves around the character of Shiva (Mithun Chakraborty), who is a loyal and fearless servant to a wealthy and influential family. He is deeply devoted to the family's elderly matriarch, Thakurain (Nirupa Roy), and her grandson, Shakti (Amrish Puri).

Trouble brews in the household when a cunning and treacherous relative named Sher Singh (Prem Chopra) plots to seize the family's wealth and property. Sher Singh is determined to eliminate Shiva, who stands in his way as a loyal and protective figure.

Amidst a series of dramatic events, Shiva is framed for a crime he did not commit, leading to his arrest and imprisonment. However, his commitment to justice and loyalty to the family remain unwavering.

While in prison, Shiva faces numerous challenges and obstacles, but he never loses hope. He eventually manages to escape and returns to Thakurain's estate to expose Sher Singh's deceitful intentions and bring him to justice.

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a story of honor, loyalty, and the battle between good and evil. Mithun Chakraborty's performance as Shiva is a key highlight of the film, and it combines elements of action, drama, and suspense. The movie also explores themes of family values and the resilience of the human spirit in the face of adversity.

Charnon Ki Saugandh (1988) Part -1 | Mithun Chakraborty, Amrita Singh | Blockbuster Action Movie

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a Bollywood movie released in 1988, featuring Mithun Chakraborty in the lead role. Directed by K. Bapaiah, the film falls into the action and drama genres. Here's a brief synopsis of the movie:

The film revolves around the character of Shiva (Mithun Chakraborty), who is a loyal and fearless servant to a wealthy and influential family. He is deeply devoted to the family's elderly matriarch, Thakurain (Nirupa Roy), and her grandson, Shakti (Amrish Puri).

Trouble brews in the household when a cunning and treacherous relative named Sher Singh (Prem Chopra) plots to seize the family's wealth and property. Sher Singh is determined to eliminate Shiva, who stands in his way as a loyal and protective figure.

Amidst a series of dramatic events, Shiva is framed for a crime he did not commit, leading to his arrest and imprisonment. However, his commitment to justice and loyalty to the family remain unwavering.

While in prison, Shiva faces numerous challenges and obstacles, but he never loses hope. He eventually manages to escape and returns to Thakurain's estate to expose Sher Singh's deceitful intentions and bring him to justice.

"Charnon Ki Saugandh" is a story of honor, loyalty, and the battle between good and evil. Mithun Chakraborty's performance as Shiva is a key highlight of the film, and it combines elements of action, drama, and suspense. The movie also explores themes of family values and the resilience of the human spirit in the face of adversity.
